==English==
===Adjective===
'''equiangular'''

#{{geometry}} Referring to a [[polygon]] all of whose [[interior angle]]s are equal.  This is not necessarily a [[regular polygon]] since that would also be [[equilateral]]; a [[rectangle]] is equiangular but not equilateral unless it is a [[square]].

